{"data":[{"date":"07:41 14/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan (16h00 ng\u00e0y 14/8): Chinh ph\u1ee5c th\u1eed th\u00e1ch","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-16h00-ngay-148-chien-thang-ngay-ra-quan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>NHM n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 \u0111ang r\u1ea5t ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ASIAD v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u nay gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan.</h2><h2>Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam &ndash; Khi kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 th\u1eed th\u00e1ch</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i ch\u01b0a khi n\u00e0o, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo l\u1ea1i nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng cao nh\u01b0 hi\u1ec7n nay. \u0110\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 b\u1edfi h\u1ecd v\u1eeba b\u01b0\u1edbc ra t\u1eeb VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 v\u1edbi danh hi\u1ec7u \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim \u00e1 qu\u00e2n gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u01a1n th\u1ebf n\u1eefa, th\u00e0nh t\u00edch v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Palestine, Oman v\u00e0 Uzbekistan c\u00e0ng c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 th\u00eam s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng k\u1ef3 ASIAD tr\u01b0\u1edbc, l\u00fac n\u00e0y th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e0nh 1 trong hai t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D. &nbsp;<o:p></o:p>D\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 kh\u00e1 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec1u, c\u00f3 \u00fd th\u1ee9c k\u1ef7 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan (16h00 ng\u00e0y 148) h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan (16h00 ng\u00e0y 148) h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-16h00-ngay-148-chien-thang-ngay-ra-quan.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n ASIAD</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf nh\u1eefng b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i Indonesia d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m suy y\u1ebfu tinh th\u1ea7n c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c ch\u00e0ng trai \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, trong 3 ng\u00e0y c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t Indonesia, HLV Park Hang Seo c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u00fang m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp tr\u00ean s\u00e2n \u0111\u00fang ngh\u0129a, nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 s\u00e2n c\u1ecf nh\u00e2n t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u 7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi, do s\u00e2n c\u1ecf m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ee7a Samsung t\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Java ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng qu\u00e1 th\u1ea5p. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 &lsquo;t\u1eadp chay&rsquo; tr\u00ean m\u1eb7t xi m\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p Olympic Pakistan v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay (14/8).<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u an \u1ee7i l\u00e0 trong ho\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1eabn t\u1ef1 b\u1ea3o nhau gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tinh th\u1ea7n l\u1ea1c quan v\u00e0 l\u00f2ng quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m cho m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chinh ph\u1ee5c nh\u1eefng t\u1ea5m huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng ASIAD \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i c\u1ee7a NHM.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ebfn v\u1edbi ASIAD, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n kh\u00e1i ni\u1ec7m &lsquo;thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 c\u1ecd x\u00e1t h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi kinh nghi\u1ec7m&rsquo;. Ng\u00f4i v\u1ecb \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim \u00e1 qu\u00e2n U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 kh\u00f4ng cho ph\u00e9p h\u1ecd thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i. R\u1ea5t may \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n n\u00e0y v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang seo c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1ng ng\u1ea1i v\u00e0 h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u1eefng g\u00ec h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o may m\u1eafn.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-va-ket-qua-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-472-193926.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-u23-viet-nam-ket-qua-tai-asiad-2018-472-193923.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i Asiad 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Gi\u1ea3i m\u00e3 &lsquo;\u1ea9n s\u1ed1&rsquo; Olympic Pakistan<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Pakistan c\u00f2n kh\u00e1 l\u1ea1 l\u1eabm v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u1edfi su\u1ed1t 3 n\u0103m qua, h\u1ecd b\u1ecb c\u1ea5m thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf sau \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t t\u1eeb L\u0110B\u0110 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi FIFA.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">3 n\u0103m c\u0169ng l\u00e0 kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Pakistan &lsquo;\u00e2m th\u1ea7m luy\u1ec7n c\u00f4ng&rsquo; \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi ASIAD 2018 - gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ea5p ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc Nam \u00c1 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tham d\u1ef1.&nbsp; <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khan hi\u1ebfm th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y song r\u1ea5t may m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9n b\u0103ng ghi h\u00ecnh c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Pakistan t\u1ea1i Bahrain m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ngu\u1ed3n th\u00f4ng tin qu\u00fd gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1eafm r\u00f5 th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea1n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 ban \u0111\u1ea7u, Pakistan kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00f3n hung tin khi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Kaleemullah Khan kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t. Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 25 tu\u1ed5i xin h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n mu\u1ed9n v\u00ec v\u01b0\u1edbng b\u1eadn th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, nh\u01b0ng b\u1ecb L\u0110B\u0110 Pakistan t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i v\u00ec cho r\u1eb1ng anh kh\u00f4ng coi tr\u1ecdng m\u00e0u c\u1edd s\u1eafc \u00e1o.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"DT Olympic Pakistan\" title=\"\u0110T Olympic Pakistan\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/Cac-doi-thu-tai-ASIAD-cua-DT-Olympic-Viet-Nam-manh-yeu-the-nao-hinh-anh.jpeg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110T Olympic Pakistan kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u1ea1i ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Olympic Pakistan c\u00f3 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y 20 tu\u1ed5i. Ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Saddam Hussain. &nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hussain hi\u1ec7n ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng cho Larnaka Gencler Birligi S.K, CLB c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ea3o S\u00edp. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i (c\u00f9ng Yousuf Butt) trong l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng 20 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Olympic Pakistan. T\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 25 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u 19 tr\u1eadn cho \u0110T Pakistan.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00ecn chung, \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Olympic Pakistan ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c. C\u00f2n v\u1ec1 kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u hay b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 th\u1ee9 g\u00ec kh\u00e1c n\u1eefa, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i h\u1ecd kh\u00f3 m\u00e0 b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Th\u00e0nh t\u00edch g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y c\u0169ng kh\u00e1 khi\u00eam nh\u01b0\u1eddng. H\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e1 4 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u00eam ASIAD v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 1 th\u1eafng, 2 h\u00f2a v\u00e0 1 thua.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u00e0 c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 HLV Park Hang Seo t\u1ef1 tin h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2. Trong cu\u1ed9c trao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1edbi b\u00e1o ch\u00ed tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Pakistan v\u1edbi s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 3 - 4 - 3. \u0110\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 qu\u00e1 l\u1ea1 l\u1eabm v\u1edbi \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng, c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c c\u1ea3nh gi\u00e1c. Ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n&nbsp;\u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng, ch\u00fang ta ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1i c\u00e1ch Palestien hay Uzbekistan \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf&nbsp;gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y ch\u01b0a l\u00e2u.T\u1ef1 tin nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 quan, t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng s\u01a1 h\u1edf, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u1eb7t h\u00e1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 nh\u01b0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng.<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:&#xA;115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n, nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan: 2-0<br>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:&nbsp;</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div>+ Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam: B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng; Duy M\u1ea1nh, \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng, V\u0103n Thanh, V\u0103n H\u1eadu; \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft; Quang H\u1ea3i, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Anh \u0110\u1ee9c.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>+ Olympic Pakistan: Saqib Hanif; Mohsin Ali, Umar Hayat, Mohammad Sohail, Muhammad Bilal; Khan Niazi, Saddam Hussain, Basit Amin, Mehmood Khan; Mohammad Riaz, Maqbool.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-khi-thay-park-da-lo-het-168-194191.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-khi-thay-park-da-lo-het.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-khi-thay-park-da-lo-het-168-194191.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD: Khi th\u1ea7y Park \u0111\u00e3 lo h\u1ebft</span><br>\r\n\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD trong \u00edt ng\u00e0y n\u1eefa. V\u00e0 l\u00fac n\u00e0y NHM c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0, khi m\u00e0 HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 lo...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2343","checkdouble":"194428"},{"date":"07:38 14/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Dynamo Kiev vs Slavia Praha 23h30 ng\u00e0y 14/8 (Champions League 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/nhan-dinh-dynamo-kiev-vs-slavia-praha-23h30-ngay-148-champions-league-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Dynamo Kiev vs Slavia Praha l\u00fac 23h30 ng\u00e0y 14/8 (V\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i c\u00fap C1/Champions League 2018/19): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Dynamo Kiev vs Slavia Praha 23h30 ng\u00e0y 148 c\u00fap C1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Dynamo Kiev vs Slavia Praha 23h30 ng\u00e0y 148 c\u00fap C1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/Dynamo-Kiev-vs-Slavia-Praha.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Dynamo Kiev vs Slavia Praha</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>Dynamo Kiev vs Slavia Praha: 1-0<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>Trong tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, do ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch n\u00ean Dynamo Kiev ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng ch\u01a1i ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat s\u01a1 h\u1edf \u1edf h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Ukraine b\u1ecb g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a v\u00e0o ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. Tuy v\u1eady, v\u1edbi v\u1ed1n li\u1ebfng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch, Dynamo Kiev chi\u1ebfm ch\u00fat \u01b0u th\u1ebf trong tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh h\u1ecd lu\u00f4n r\u1ea5t bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng \u01b0u th\u1ebf v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t s\u00e2n b\u00e3i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. 6 tr\u1eadn s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t th\u00ec h\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh 5 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1ec1 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n v\u00e0 4 l\u1ea7n theo ch\u00e2u \u00c1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Ukraine lu\u00f4n bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh bi\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1eddi: g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 - ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ngc\u00f2n khi ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng y\u1ebfu, Dynamo Kiev ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng \u00e1p \u0111\u1eb7t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn, Slavia Praha \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1edbi 7 tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y (6 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng). Nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i \u1edf tr\u00ean, Dynamo Kiev khi g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u00ec h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng, \u01b0u ti\u00ean ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Slavia Praha c\u0169ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t khi gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ea3 5 tr\u1eadn ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch v\u1eeba qua. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, Kiev c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua th\u1eed th\u00e1ch n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng playoff song s\u1ebd v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2342","checkdouble":"194429"},{"date":"07:51 14/08","title":"Roma chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u201cb\u00e1o th\u00f9\u201d Barca th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ngc","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/12/6/roma-chuan-bi-bao-thu-barca-thanh-cong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ef1u th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n David Seaman th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng ra m\u1eb7t khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u00e2m ph\u1ee5c kh\u1ea9u ph\u1ee5c trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi g\u1eb7p nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Manchester City.\r\n\r\n</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1ed7i hi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a Raheem Sterling v\u00e0 Bernardo Silva nh\u1ea5m ch\u00ecm Emirates v\u00e0 x\u00f3a nh\u00f2a m\u1ecdi s\u1ef1 h\u1ee9ng kh\u1edfi d\u01b0\u1edbi tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n HLV Unai Emery. Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u00e2m ph\u1ee5c kh\u1ea9u ph\u1ee5c ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n Premier League 2018/19 cho th\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t Arsenal d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u bi\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec3n t\u00edch c\u1ef1c so v\u1edbi th\u1eddi Gi\u00e1o S\u01b0 Arsene Wenger.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Arsenal vs Man City M\u00e8o v\u1eabn ho\u00e0n m\u00e8o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Arsenal vs Man City M\u00e8o v\u1eabn ho\u00e0n m\u00e8o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/huyen-thoai-ngan-ngam-arsenal-meo-van-hoan-meo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>D\u01b0 \u00e2m Arsenal vs Man City</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i David Seaman c\u0169ng nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y v\u00e0 t\u1ecf r\u00f5 s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn thua b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 55 tu\u1ed5i: &ldquo;Ch\u00fang ta cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u1eabn ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t Arsenal x\u01b0a c\u0169 nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e0 th\u00f4i. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u00f4 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c \u1edf h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i th\u1ea5y \u0111\u00e1ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Ainsley Maitland-Niles khi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean b\u1ecb c\u00f4 l\u1eadp v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ai h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3, th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean b\u1ecb Kyle Walker r\u1ed3i Riyad Mahrez thi nhau h\u00e0nh cho ra b\u00e3. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, hai h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh l\u1ea1i d\u00e2ng l\u00ean qu\u00e1 cao m\u00e0 th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng, ch\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i s\u1ebd ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u00f9i xu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. C\u00e1ch ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Emery r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng lo ng\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea5y.&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Arsenal ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 th\u00eam tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e0nh \u00edt d\u1eef nhi\u1ec1u khi h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m Chelsea trong tr\u1eadn derby London. Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Maurizio Sarri tr\u00e1i l\u1ea1i m\u1edbi c\u00f3 m\u00e0n kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng su\u00f4n s\u1ebb v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 ho\u00e0nh tr\u00e1ng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Huddersfield Town.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-02-man-city-binh-moi-nhung-ruou-chua-moi-172-194363.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/arsenal-02-man-city-binh-moi-nhung-ruou-chua-moi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-02-man-city-binh-moi-nhung-ruou-chua-moi-172-194363.html\">Arsenal 0-2 Man City: B\u00ecnh m\u1edbi nh\u01b0ng r\u01b0\u1ee3u ch\u01b0a m\u1edbi</span><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Unai Emery \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City. V\u00e0 r\u00f5...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2341","checkdouble":"194430"},{"date":"07:52 14/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Dinamo Zagreb vs Astana 01h00 ng\u00e0y 15/8 (Champions League 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/nhan-dinh-dinamo-zagreb-vs-astana-01h00-ngay-158-champions-league-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Dinamo Zagreb vs Astana l\u00fac 01h00 ng\u00e0y 15/8 (V\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i c\u00fap C1/Champions League 2018/19): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Dinamo Zagreb vs Astana 1h00 ng\u00e0y 158 Champions League h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Dinamo Zagreb vs Astana 1h00 ng\u00e0y 158 Champions League h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/Dinamo-Zagreb-vs-Astana.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Dinamo Zagreb vs Astana</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>Dinamo Zagreb vs Astana: 3-1<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>\u1ede tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, khi l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i Kazakhstan, Dinamo Zagreb b\u1ecb x\u1ebfp \u1edf c\u1eeda d\u01b0\u1edbi. Tuy v\u1eady, v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00e1p ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Croatia \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 mang l\u1ea1i \u01b0u th\u1ebf l\u1edbn cho th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Nenad Bjelica b\u1edfi \u1edf tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1, ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n 1 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed thua v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u, Dinamo Zagreb v\u1eabn gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng playoff.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 l\u00fd, Dinamo Zagreb kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng song gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n v\u1eabn \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Croatia. Ngo\u00e0i \u01b0u th\u1ebf s\u00e2n b\u00e3i, h\u1ecd c\u00f2n \u0111ang th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao v\u1edbi m\u1ea1ch 13 tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i (c\u1ea3 giao h\u1eefu). <br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea1i s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, Dinamo Zagreb lu\u00f4n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5. V\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 2, khi ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Hapoel Beer Sheva (Israel), Dinamo Zagreb \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e8 b\u1eb9p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 5-0. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh th\u00eam 1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi Astana, th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-2 \u1edf tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi cu\u1ed9c ch\u01a1i. \u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 hy v\u1ecdng l\u1eadp ra k\u1ef3 t\u00edch \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Kazakhstan \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng song tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, Astana \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng r\u1ea5t t\u1ec7. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i gi\u1eefa 2 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00eam nay, t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 t\u1ed5ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u1ea1i \u1edf m\u1ee9c kh\u00e1 cao. Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng 5/7 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Dinamo Zagreb k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 3 b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00c0NH T\u00cdCH \u0110\u1ed0I \u0110\u1ea6U<br>\r\n- \u1ede tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, Dinamo Zagreb \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Astana.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH D\u1ef0 KI\u1ebeN<br>\r\n+ Dinamo Zagreb (4-2-3-1): Zagorac - Stojanovic, Theophile-Catherine, Dilaver, Leovac - Gojak, Sunjic - Hajrovic, Orsic, Olmo - Budimir.<br>\r\n+ Astana (4-1-4-1): Eric - Rukavina, Postnikov, Anicic, Shomko - Maevskiy - Tomasov, Kleinheisler, Muzhikov, Henrique - Kabananga</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2340","checkdouble":"194431"},{"date":"07:57 14/08","title":"Xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/xem-truc-tiep-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-o-dau.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00e2u h\u1ecfi \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u0111\u1eb7t ra l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 s\u1ebd theo d\u00f5i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u khi VTV kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD.\r\n\r\n</h2><h2>Xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u?</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i, do m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed ch\u00e0o b\u00e1n b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD 2018 qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u2018b\u00e1n l\u1ebb\u2019 m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u00ean \u0111\u00e0i truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh Vi\u1ec7t Nam VTV \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng mua b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c NHM ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 theo d\u00f5i nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo th\u00f4ng qua internet. Song NHM s\u1ebd xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u?<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/Xem-truc-tiep-Olympic-Viet-Nam-vs-Olympic-Pakistan-o-dau-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>NHM c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan tr\u00ean trang vidio.com.</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 theo d\u00f5i mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u00f4ng qua website vidio.com.\u00a0<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 website ph\u00e1t tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a ASIAD 2018 \u1edf t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c m\u00f4n. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xem vidio.com l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfn t\u00edch c\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c k\u00ec ASIAD tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Website n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 chi\u1ebfu tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam trong c\u00e1c ng\u00e0y t\u1eeb 10/8 \u0111\u1ebfn 12/8 v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3n h\u1ed3i t\u00edch c\u1ef1c t\u1eeb c\u00e1c kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o l\u00fac 16h ng\u00e0y 14/8 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, website vidio.com d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edf m\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam g\u1eb7p Pakistan./.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:\n10.0pt;font-family:\" new=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-16h00-ngay-148-chien-thang-ngay-ra-quan-168-194428.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-16h00-ngay-148-chien-thang-ngay-ra-quan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-16h00-ngay-148-chien-thang-ngay-ra-quan-168-194428.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan (16h00 ng\u00e0y 14/8): Chinh ph\u1ee5c th\u1eed th\u00e1ch</span><br>\r\nNHM n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 \u0111ang r\u1ea5t ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ASIAD v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u nay gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div>\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2339","checkdouble":"194432"},{"date":"08:29 14/08","title":"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i ng\u00e1n ng\u1ea9m Arsenal \u201cm\u00e8o v\u1eabn ho\u00e0n m\u00e8o\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/huyen-thoai-ngan-ngam-arsenal-meo-van-hoan-meo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ef1u th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n David Seaman th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng ra m\u1eb7t khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u00e2m ph\u1ee5c kh\u1ea9u ph\u1ee5c trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi g\u1eb7p nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Manchester City.\r\n\r\n</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1ed7i hi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a Raheem Sterling v\u00e0 Bernardo Silva nh\u1ea5m ch\u00ecm Emirates v\u00e0 x\u00f3a nh\u00f2a m\u1ecdi s\u1ef1 h\u1ee9ng kh\u1edfi d\u01b0\u1edbi tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n HLV Unai Emery. Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u00e2m ph\u1ee5c kh\u1ea9u ph\u1ee5c ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n Premier League 2018/19 cho th\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t Arsenal d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u bi\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec3n t\u00edch c\u1ef1c so v\u1edbi th\u1eddi Gi\u00e1o S\u01b0 Arsene Wenger.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Arsenal vs Man City M\u00e8o v\u1eabn ho\u00e0n m\u00e8o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Arsenal vs Man City M\u00e8o v\u1eabn ho\u00e0n m\u00e8o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/huyen-thoai-ngan-ngam-arsenal-meo-van-hoan-meo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>D\u01b0 \u00e2m Arsenal vs Man City</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i David Seaman c\u0169ng nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y v\u00e0 t\u1ecf r\u00f5 s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn thua b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 55 tu\u1ed5i: &ldquo;Ch\u00fang ta cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u1eabn ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t Arsenal x\u01b0a c\u0169 nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e0 th\u00f4i. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u00f4 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c \u1edf h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i th\u1ea5y \u0111\u00e1ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Ainsley Maitland-Niles khi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean b\u1ecb c\u00f4 l\u1eadp v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ai h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3, th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean b\u1ecb Kyle Walker r\u1ed3i Riyad Mahrez thi nhau h\u00e0nh cho ra b\u00e3. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, hai h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh l\u1ea1i d\u00e2ng l\u00ean qu\u00e1 cao m\u00e0 th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng, ch\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i s\u1ebd ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u00f9i xu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. C\u00e1ch ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Emery r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng lo ng\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea5y.&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Arsenal ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 th\u00eam tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e0nh \u00edt d\u1eef nhi\u1ec1u khi h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m Chelsea trong tr\u1eadn derby London. Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Maurizio Sarri tr\u00e1i l\u1ea1i m\u1edbi c\u00f3 m\u00e0n kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng su\u00f4n s\u1ebb v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 ho\u00e0nh tr\u00e1ng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Huddersfield Town.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-02-man-city-binh-moi-nhung-ruou-chua-moi-172-194363.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/arsenal-02-man-city-binh-moi-nhung-ruou-chua-moi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-02-man-city-binh-moi-nhung-ruou-chua-moi-172-194363.html\">Arsenal 0-2 Man City: B\u00ecnh m\u1edbi nh\u01b0ng r\u01b0\u1ee3u ch\u01b0a m\u1edbi</span><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Unai Emery \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City. V\u00e0 r\u00f5...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2338","checkdouble":"194433"},{"date":"08:11 14/08","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 14/8: M.U s\u1eafp ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng trong m\u01a1","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-ngay-148-mu-sap-hoan-tat-ban-hop-dong-trong-mo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 14/8.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Barca \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u00e1n Dembele.</strong> Barcelona s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng l\u1eafng nghe nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb d\u00e0nh cho Ousmane Dembele. Sao tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p tr\u1ea3i qua m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i khi ch\u00ecm trong nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 phong \u0111\u1ed9 b\u1ea5t \u1ed5n. Barca mu\u1ed1n thanh l\u00fd Dembele \u0111\u1ec3 thu v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>M.U s\u1eafp ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng trong m\u01a1. </strong>Man United t\u1ef1 tin David de Gea s\u1ebd k\u00fd v\u00e0o h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi thay cho giao k\u00e8o c\u0169 c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y 1 n\u0103m. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 180 ngh\u00ecn b\u1ea3ng/ tu\u1ea7n t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Old Trafford v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng g\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd \u1edf l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 148 MU s\u1eafp gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi De Gea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 148 MU s\u1eafp gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi De Gea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/21/Diem-tin-bong-da-sang-ngay-148-MU-sap-gia-han-voi-De-Gea-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">M.U t\u1ef1 tin gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng De Gea</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Atletico v\u00e0 Dortmund quan t\u00e2m sao Tottenham. </strong>V\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Serge Aurier t\u1ea1i Tottenham b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 n\u1ed5i l\u00ean c\u1ee7a Kieran Trippier. Hi\u1ec7n c\u1ea3 Atletico Madrid v\u00e0 Dortmund \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Liverpool xem x\u00e9t b\u00e1n Klavan. </strong>Liverpool \u0111ang xem x\u00e9t kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 Ragnar Klavan ra \u0111i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u1eeda s\u1ed5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u00f3ng l\u1ea1i v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng 8. L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf \u0111ang t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch tinh gi\u1ea3n bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf v\u00e0 Klavan n\u1eb1m trong danh s\u00e1ch n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Modric \u1edf l\u1ea1i Real b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p tin \u0111\u1ed3n Inter.</strong> Luka Modric \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Real Madrid d\u1ef1 tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u1edbi Atletico Madrid. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Inter Milan \u0111ang g\u1eedi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ch\u00e0o m\u1eddi h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn cho tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Croatia. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn t\u1eeb Real, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Modric v\u1eabn \u1edf l\u1ea1i m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Luka Modric\" title=\"Luka Modric\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/Chi-75-trieu-bang,-Real-Madrid-mua-Christian-Eriksen-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Real quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t Modric v\u00e0o tay Inter</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>B\u1ed9 ba \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh theo \u0111u\u1ed5i sao tr\u1ebb Real. </strong>3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Anh l\u00e0 Middlebrough, Derby v\u00e0 Aston Villa \u0111\u1ec1u d\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m cho Martin Odegaard. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 19 tu\u1ed5i \u01b0u ti\u00ean n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh l\u00e0m b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 n\u1ebfu r\u1eddi Real song chi\u1ec1u mua c\u00e1c CLB Premier League \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3ng l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nInter m\u01b0\u1ee3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ef1u sao tr\u1ebb Barca. </strong>Keita Balde m\u1edbi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Inter Milan d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n 1 n\u0103m t\u1eeb Monaco. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia c\u00e0i v\u00e0o h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o t\u1ea1i Barcelona trong 7 n\u0103m (2004 t\u1edbi 2011) v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 34 tri\u1ec7u Euro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Gameiro r\u1eddi Atletico gia nh\u1eadp Valencia. </strong>Valencia th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Kevin Gameiro t\u1eeb Atletico Madrid. \u0110\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 bi\u1ec7t danh \"B\u1ea7y d\u01a1i\" \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i chi ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 16 tri\u1ec7u Euro. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2337","checkdouble":"194435"},{"date":"08:15 14/08","title":"C\u1ef1u HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/12/cuu-hlv-truong-dt-viet-nam-dat-niem-tin-vao-thay-tro-park-hang-seo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, c\u1ef1u HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam, \u00f4ng Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ASIAD s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.</h2><h2>HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam&nbsp; <o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o l\u00fac 16h00 chi\u1ec1u nay, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Olympic Pakistan t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng D, m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/hlv-park-hang-seo-khong-ngai-doi-dau-dt-olympic-han-quoc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Pakistan</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng tin t\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n n\u00e0y chia s\u1ebb: &quot;Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u hanh th\u00f4ng. Pakistan kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh. G\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu l\u00e0 thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n&quot;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, v\u1ecb c\u1ef1u HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00fat lo ng\u1ea1i v\u1edbi th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 khi h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f3 kh\u00ed h\u1eadu n\u1eafng n\u00f3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;\u1ede gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0o, th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng. Ch\u00fang ta v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua giai \u0111o\u1ea1n V.League kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t. C\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadp trung ngay, l\u1ea1i thi \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1ea3i &quot;T\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng&quot; v\u1eeba qua, n\u00ean t\u00f4i lo h\u1ecd b\u1ecb b\u00e0o m\u00f2n&quot;, HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng chia s\u1ebb.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i ra nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n \u0111ang d\u1eabn d\u1eaft CLB Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh c\u00f2n chia s\u1ebb th\u00eam v\u1ec1 c\u00e1ch ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Theo \u0111\u00f3 v\u1ecb n\u00e0y tin t\u01b0\u1edfng HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Olympic Pakistan s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 16h00 chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Wibawa Mukti (Cikarang). Bongda24h s\u1ebd t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u00e0y, mong b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u00f3n xem.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-16h00-ngay-148-chien-thang-ngay-ra-quan-168-194428.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-16h00-ngay-148-chien-thang-ngay-ra-quan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-16h00-ngay-148-chien-thang-ngay-ra-quan-168-194428.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan (16h00 ng\u00e0y 14/8): Chinh ph\u1ee5c th\u1eed th\u00e1ch</span><br>\r\nNHM n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 \u0111ang r\u1ea5t ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ASIAD v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u nay gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/xem-truc-tiep-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-o-dau-168-194432.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/xem-truc-tiep-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-o-dau.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/xem-truc-tiep-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-o-dau-168-194432.html\">Xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u?</span><br>\r\nC\u00e2u h\u1ecfi \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u0111\u1eb7t ra l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 s\u1ebd theo d\u00f5i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u khi VTV kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</span></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2336","checkdouble":"194436"},{"date":"08:49 14/08","title":"Van Dijk m\u1edf l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i t\u00e2n binh Alisson","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/van-dijk-alisson-se-giup-liverpool-chinh-phuc-premier-league.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Van Dijk tin r\u1eb1ng s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson Becker s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Liverpool \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec1 ra \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay.</h2><h2>Van Dijk khen ng\u1ee3i Alisson</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Alisson kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea5t di\u1ec5n trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Liverpool tr\u01b0\u1edbc West Ham t\u1ea1i Anfield cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n qua. \u201cB\u00faa t\u1ea1\u201d kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 tung ra \u0111\u00fang 2 c\u00fa s\u00fat tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch trong tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a h\u00e8 v\u1eeba qua, Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Alisson t\u1eeb Roma v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c l\u00e0 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn h\u01a1n cho khung th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Liverpool khi c\u1ea3 Loris Karius v\u00e0 Simon Mignolet \u0111\u1ec1u g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Van Dijk m\u1edf l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Van Dijk m\u1edf l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/van-dijk-alisson-se-giup-liverpool-chinh-phuc-premier-league.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Van DIjk khen ng\u1ee3i t\u00e2n binh Alisson c\u1ee7a Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0 Liverpool s\u1ebd c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng th\u1eed th\u00e1ch kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n h\u01a1n West Ham, Van Dijk v\u1eabn tin r\u1eb1ng Alisson s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cAlisson \u0111\u00e3 th\u00edch nghi r\u1ea5t nhanh ch\u00f3ng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 c\u00e1 t\u00ednh v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap \u00edch r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u1ec9 huy ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t t\u1eeb ph\u00eda sau. S\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y gi\u00fap ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y an t\u00e2m h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i ch\u00e2n t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tri\u1ec3n khai b\u00f3ng ngay t\u1eeb tuy\u1ebfn d\u01b0\u1edbi. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n trong su\u1ed1t giai \u0111o\u1ea1n giao h\u1eefu v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 nhu\u1ea7n nhuy\u1ec5n h\u01a1n. V\u1eabn c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Van Dijk gi\u1eef \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00e2n tr\u00ean m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ea5t</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu Liverpool mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea1t t\u1edbi th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng m\u00f9a n\u00e0y th\u00ec c\u1ea3 Alisson v\u00e0 Van Dijk \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3ng m\u1ed9t vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng. HLV Jurgen Klopp tin r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh cho nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn. Nh\u01b0ng Van Dijk kh\u00f4ng t\u1ef1 tin \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ebf.<br>\r\n<em><br>\r\n\u201c\u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadp trung c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea1nh tranh \u1edf t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u1eeba v\u1eb7n\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Liverpool:<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-cai-ten-tiep-theo-roi-liverpool-o-he-2018-172-194419.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! C\u00e1i t\u00ean ti\u1ebfp theo r\u1eddi Liverpool \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-klopp-noi-gi-ve-co-hoi-vo-dich-nha-cua-liverpool-172-194412.html\">HLV Klopp n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch NHA c\u1ee7a Liverpool?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nXu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2335","checkdouble":"194437"},{"date":"08:31 14/08","title":"HLV Pakistan n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc cu\u1ed9c so t\u00e0i v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/14/hlv-pakistan-noi-gi-truoc-cuoc-so-tai-voi-olympic-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng D, m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018, HLV Jose Antonio Noguira c\u1ee7a Pakistan \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\r\n\r\n</h2><h2>HLV Pakistan n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc cu\u1ed9c so t\u00e0i v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng D, m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018. V\u1edbi l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec1u, kinh nghi\u1ec7m h\u01a1n l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1eebng v\u00e0o t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u0129 nhi\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Pakistan n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc cu\u1ed9c so t\u00e0i v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Pakistan n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc cu\u1ed9c so t\u00e0i v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/HLV-PAKISTAN-5-8912-1534142888-8699-1534156883.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Olympic Pakistan (gi\u1eefa) th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00ednh HLV Jose Antonio Noguira, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Olympic Pakistan th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn: &ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 xem b\u0103ng h\u00ecnh c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. C\u00e1c b\u1ea1n \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh \u1edf l\u1ee9a tu\u1ed5i 23. \u0110\u1ed9i c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 g\u1eafn k\u1ebft v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, HLV Park Hang-seo l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian g\u1eafn b\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 d\u00e0i \u0111\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7&rdquo;.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-va-ket-qua-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-472-193926.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-u23-viet-nam-ket-qua-tai-asiad-2018-472-193923.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i Asiad 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb n\u00e0y c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 g\u1eb7p kh\u00f4ng \u00edt th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c do ba n\u0103m qua kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1 gi\u1ea3i qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf do \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t c\u1ea5m thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eeb FIFA.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil n\u00f3i th\u00eam: &quot;\u0110\u00fang l\u00e0 ba&nbsp;n\u0103m qua Pakistan kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c n\u00e0o. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng gh\u00ea g\u1edbm. T\u00f4i k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Pakistan v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng l\u1ea1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y t\u1eeb c\u00e1c l\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft t\u00f4i c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Jose Antonio Noguira c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn Olympic Pakistan kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb7t n\u1eb7ng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u1edf gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd tranh t\u00e0i v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau t\u00edch lu\u1ef9 kinh nghi\u1ec7m l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1eabn s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n cao nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u1ea3 quan trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ASIAD.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Olympic Pakistan s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 16h00 chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Wibawa Mukti (Cikarang). Bongda24h s\u1ebd t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u00e0y, mong b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u00f3n xem.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-16h00-ngay-148-chien-thang-ngay-ra-quan-168-194428.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-16h00-ngay-148-chien-thang-ngay-ra-quan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-16h00-ngay-148-chien-thang-ngay-ra-quan-168-194428.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan (16h00 ng\u00e0y 14/8): Chinh ph\u1ee5c th\u1eed th\u00e1ch</span><br>\r\nNHM n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 \u0111ang r\u1ea5t ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ASIAD v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u nay gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/xem-truc-tiep-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-o-dau-168-194432.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/xem-truc-tiep-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-o-dau.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/xem-truc-tiep-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-pakistan-o-dau-168-194432.html\">Xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u?</span><br>\r\nC\u00e2u h\u1ecfi \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u0111\u1eb7t ra l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 s\u1ebd theo d\u00f5i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Pakistan \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u khi VTV kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2334","checkdouble":"194438"},{"date":"21:43 13/08","title":"Bayern Munich nh\u1eadn tin c\u1ef1c vui t\u1eeb tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/bayern-munich-nhan-tin-cuc-vui-tu-tru-cot.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>David Alaba ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf d\u00e2y ch\u1eb1ng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn t\u1eeb ph\u00eda HLV Niko Kovac.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">David Alaba d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBayern Munich \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n Eintracht Frankfurt trong tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c, v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i c\u00f9ng quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1ea5t cao, \u201cH\u00f9m x\u00e1m\u201d \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 5-0.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"David Alaba ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, HLV Niko Kovac l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"David Alaba ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, HLV Niko Kovac l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/David-Alaba-chan-thuong,-HLV-Niko-Kovac-len-tieng-hinh-anh.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Alaba d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc\u00a0Eintracht Frankfurt</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Robert Lewandowski \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u00fa hat-trick. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc\u00a0 Eintracht Frankfurt gi\u00fap \u201cH\u00f9m x\u00e1m\u201d h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1eaft.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 David Alaba ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Eintracht Frankfurt, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00c1o g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 sau pha va ch\u1ea1m m\u1ea1nh v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n cho r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ee9t d\u00e2y ch\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0i th\u00e1ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Bayern n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Alaba</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00c1o, HLV Niko Kovac \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng. David Alaba ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf d\u00e2y ch\u1eb1ng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn t\u1eeb ph\u00eda t\u00e2n HLV c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alba\" title=\"Alba\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/bayern-munich-nhan-tin-cuc-vui-tu-tru-cot.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Alaba kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ee9t d\u00e2y ch\u1eb1ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\"Alaba g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Eintracht Frankfurt, \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Alaba \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c ki\u1ec3m tra, \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 y t\u1ebf k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u00e2y ch\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i t\u00f4i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u bao nhi\u00eau l\u00e2u, Alaba v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n th\u00eam nh\u1eefng bu\u1ed5i ki\u1ec3m tra \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBayern Munich s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 danh hi\u1ec7u Bundesliga v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 24 th\u00e1ng 8, \u1edf tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n Bundesliga 2018/19 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Hoffenheim.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2333","checkdouble":"194414"},{"date":"22:01 13/08","title":"Kante n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u1edbi d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Sarri?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/kante-noi-gi-ve-vi-tri-moi-duoi-thoi-hlv-sarri.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>NGolo Kante ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Chelsea, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u1edbi d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Maurizio Sarri.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kante v\u00e0 vai tr\u00f2 m\u1edbi \u1edf h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 NGolo Kante th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t \u1edf h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u1edbi n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c sung m\u00e3n c\u00f9ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i th\u00f4ng minh lu\u00f4n ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh t\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 trong vai tr\u00f2 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"NGolo Kante ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"NGolo Kante ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/NGolo-Kante-phat-bieu-ve-Chelsea-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kante \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Sarri</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKante \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV Maurizio Sarri, vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a anh trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Huddersfield trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19, Kante \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i cao h\u01a1n v\u00e0 nh\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 cho Jorginho.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean \u0111\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1991 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n. Kante ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho The Blues sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1eadp \u0111\u1ea5t hi\u1ec3m h\u00f3c sau \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Willian.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, Kante ch\u1ec9 ghi 1 b\u00e0n m\u1ed7i m\u00f9a. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi vai tr\u00f2 m\u1edbi d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Sarri, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a anh \u1edf m\u00f9a 2018/19 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Kante n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u1edbi d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Sarri</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">NGolo Kante ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Chelsea, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u1edbi d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Maurizio Sarri.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kante mo ty so cho Chelsea\" title=\"Kante m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho Chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Diem-nhan-Huddersfield-vs-Chelsea-vong-1-Ngoai-hang-Anh-201819-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kante n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u1edbi \u1edf Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t HLV m\u1edbi v\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tri\u1ebft l\u00fd b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 m\u1edbi, trong c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a HLV Sarri t\u00f4i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u1edbi, t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng Chelsea s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Huddersfield, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t t\u1ed1t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. \u1ede v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p Arsenal, \u0111\u00f3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cArsenal \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u t\u00e2n binh. Mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i duy tr\u00ec s\u1ef1 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ed1t, t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng Chelsea s\u1ebd c\u00f3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2332","checkdouble":"194415"},{"date":"22:56 13/08","title":"Alan Shearer: \u201cT\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean n\u1ebfu Pogba t\u1edbi Barca\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/alan-shearer-toi-se-khong-ngac-nhien-neu-pogba-toi-barca.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Liverpool b\u00e1n Ragnar Klavan l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 CN H\u00e8 2018, s\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Nat Phillips cho ph\u00e9p c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 32 tu\u1ed5i r\u1eddi Anfield.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Klopp t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Klavan cho Newcastle</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua Ragnar Klavan kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Liverpool, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1986 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh, khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i anh c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool b\u00e1n Ragnar Klavan \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Liverpool b\u00e1n Ragnar Klavan \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Liverpool-ban-Ragnar-Klavan-o-He-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Klopp t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Klavan cho Newcastle</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0i gi\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 H\u00e8 2018 \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh ch\u1eb7n chi\u1ec1u mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, Newcastle \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 32 tu\u1ed5i, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 6 tri\u1ec7u euro mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1986, song HLV Klopp \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Matip v\u00e0 Lovren d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn HLV Klopp kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 Ragnar Klavan ra \u0111i, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 32 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Ragnar Klavan \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1986 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc West Ham \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Klopp s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Van Dijk v\u00e0 Gomez \u1edf trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7, vi\u1ec7c Matip v\u00e0 Lovren s\u1eafp tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb d\u00e0i d\u00e0i. Klavan \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Klavan</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Liverpool b\u00e1n Ragnar Klavan l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 CN H\u00e8 2018, s\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Nat Phillips cho ph\u00e9p c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 32 tu\u1ed5i r\u1eddi Anfield.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Klavan vs Aguero\" title=\"Klavan vs Aguero\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/3/19/Thong-tin-luc-luong-tran-Brighton-vs-Liverpool-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Klavan s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, sao tr\u1ebb Nat Phillips \u0111\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, HLV Klopp s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 Klavan ra \u0111i, qua \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 Italia mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 32 tu\u1ed5i, Liverpool s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 5 tri\u1ec7u euro.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Klavan th\u00ec Divock Origi v\u00e0 Sheyi Ojo c\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch r\u1eddi Anfield, b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Liverpool \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2331","checkdouble":"194416"},{"date":"22:56 13/08","title":"\"Bom x\u1ecbt\" Chelsea k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi AC Milan trong v\u00e0i gi\u1edd t\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/bom-xit-chelsea-ky-hop-dong-voi-ac-milan-trong-vai-gio-toi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Tiemoue Bakayoko t\u1edbi AC Milan \u0111ang r\u1ea5t cao, theo Goal c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u01a1i Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf Italia \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">AC Milan \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Bakayoko</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTiemoue Bakayoko \u0111ang g\u1eb7p \u00e1p l\u1ef1c c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn \u1edf Chelsea, v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c HLV Sarri s\u1edf h\u1eefu Kante, Jorginho, Fabregas, Barkley, Drinkwater v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 t\u00e2n binh Kovacic n\u1eefa, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a Bakayoko \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tiemoue Bakayoko t\u1edbi AC Milan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tiemoue Bakayoko t\u1edbi AC Milan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/20/Tiemoue-Bakayoko-toi-AC-Milan-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Tiemoue Bakayoko \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c AC Milan quan t\u00e2m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf Chelsea, AC Milan \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1994. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan \u0111ang r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ef1u sao Monaco.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/them-mot-cau-thu-sap-roi-chelsea-172-194238.html\" target=\"_blank\">Tiemoue Bakayoko t\u1edbi AC Milan</span> \u0111ang r\u1ea5t cao, theo Goal c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u01a1i Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf Italia \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, AC Milan s\u1ebd m\u01b0\u1ee3n Bakayoko m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed 5 tri\u1ec7u euro, sau \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd mua \u0111\u1ee9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19 v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed 35 tri\u1ec7u euro. Nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 AC Milan b\u1ecf ra t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 40 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Bakayoko s\u1eafp ra m\u1eaft AC Milan</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Tiemoue Bakayoko t\u1edbi AC Milan \u0111ang r\u1ea5t cao, theo Goal c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u01a1i Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf Italia \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tiemoue Bakayoko t\u1edbi AC Milan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Tiemoue Bakayoko t\u1edbi AC Milan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/9/Tiemoue-Bakayoko-toi-AC-Milan-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Bakayoko s\u1eafp k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi AC Milan</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nBakayoko \u0111\u00e3 bay t\u1edbi Milan v\u00e0o h\u00f4m qua, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Milan. Anh \u0111ang di chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i b\u1ea3n doanh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n San Siro.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Bakayoko t\u1edbi AC Milan s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 trong v\u00e0i gi\u1edd t\u1edbi. D\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng \u1edf Chelsea nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf s\u00e2n San Siro.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho AC Milan, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 v\u1edbi Chelsea \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 b\u1edfi trong tay HLV Sarri \u0111ang c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2330","checkdouble":"194417"},{"date":"23:25 13/08","title":"3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \"th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng\" c\u1ee7a Real Madrid","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/3-doi-bong-anh-muon-co-than-dong-cua-real-madrid.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Anh bao g\u1ed3m Middlebrough, Aston Villa v\u00e0 Derby County mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Martin Odegaard r\u1eddi Real Madrid \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Martin Odegaard kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng \u1edf Real</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMartin Odegaard \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u1ef1c cao, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1998 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u201cth\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng\u201d c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Na Uy, anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean tri\u1ec3n v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Odegaard bat ngo duoc dang ky da Champions League\" title=\"Odegaard b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd \u0111\u00e1 Champions League\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/9/4/Nghi-van-Zidane-lai-bi-ep-dung-Odegaard-o-Champions-League-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Odegaard kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng \u1edf Real Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Na Uy gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid t\u1eeb Stromsgodset v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1/2015. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 19 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh v\u00e0 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai g\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Bernabeu Odegaard l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, anh ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n c\u00f3 1 l\u1ea7n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i 1 c\u1ee7a Los Blancos. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1998 ra \u0111i theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nOdegaard \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real Madrid \u0111\u1ea9y t\u1edbi CLB Heerenveen c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 Lan theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m. Trong th\u1eddi gian cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1ea1i Heerenveen, sao tr\u1ebb 19 tu\u1ed5i ra s\u00e2n t\u1edbi 38 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng gi\u00fap anh tr\u1ee5 l\u1ea1i \u1edf Bernabeu.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Julen Lopetegui kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Odegaard, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 19 tu\u1ed5i ra \u0111i theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Odegaard</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Anh bao g\u1ed3m Middlebrough, Aston Villa v\u00e0 Derby County mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Martin Odegaard r\u1eddi Real Madrid \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Martin Odegaard r\u1eddi Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Martin Odegaard r\u1eddi Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/3-doi-bong-anh-muon-co-than-dong-cua-real-madrid.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Odegaard s\u1eafp t\u1edbi Anh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng CLB \u1edf n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 19 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n, qua \u0111\u00f3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh. Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Real s\u1ebd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf x\u1ee9 s\u1edf s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u1edf ch\u1ed7 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Na Uy c\u00f3 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ebfn Anh ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng hay kh\u00f4ng. Hi\u1ec7n Odegaard \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb v\u00e0 Real mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ec3 anh t\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2329","checkdouble":"194418"}]}